was a one-time thing.

00:06.341 --> 00:08.607
Why?
I didn't want
you there.

00:08.609 --> 00:10.009
You got to get to the 5,
head north

00:10.011 --> 00:11.810
toward the Canadian border.
I got you your kid back.

00:11.812 --> 00:14.413
You can be together,
but you've got to go.
Yeah, but --

00:14.415 --> 00:15.614
Now!
Okay.

00:15.616 --> 00:17.282
Parker Freeman,
from Sun of a Beach.

00:17.284 --> 00:20.219
I just want my shit back.
And maybe I'll start with this.

00:20.221 --> 00:21.554
Get out of my bar.

00:21.556 --> 00:23.155
