because of me.

00:31.032 --> 00:32.431
We're here because
you didn't have the balls

00:32.433 --> 00:34.166
to shoot your boyfriend.

00:34.168 --> 00:35.368
[ Grunts ]

00:35.370 --> 00:37.502
I'll pay you back,
plus 20.

00:37.504 --> 00:39.238
Got you now, huh?

00:39.240 --> 00:41.707
Hey, you're good at looking
after your brother, right?
Yeah.

00:41.709 --> 00:42.975
