to an attorney first.

06:08.836 --> 06:10.769
-You ready?
-Yeah.

06:10.771 --> 06:13.038
What are you doing?
You throwing everything away?

06:13.040 --> 06:15.308
Yeah.
Smurf chose it.

06:15.310 --> 06:18.043
I hate it.

06:18.045 --> 06:19.712
