Making pancakes?

06:38.866 --> 06:41.000
Yeah.

06:41.002 --> 06:42.801
Right?
Yeah.

06:42.803 --> 06:44.136
Can you make pie?

06:44.138 --> 06:45.938
How'd we go from making
pancakes to pie?

06:45.940 --> 06:47.806
I dunno,
can't be that hard.

06:47.808 --> 06:51.276
Anyway,
this is for you.

06:51.278 --> 06:53.078
Nice stack.
Where'd you get it?

06:53.080 --> 06:55.948
Just collected
some rents.

06:55.950 --> 06:58.083
It's, um,
Hamburger Hill today.

06:58.085 --> 06:59.752
Thought maybe
we could take Nick.

06:59.754 --> 07:01.620
The skate race?

07:01.622 --> 07:02.821
Yeah.

07:02.823 --> 07:04.357
