07:04.359 --> 07:05.558
11:00.

07:05.560 --> 07:06.892
Mm. No good,<i> amor.</i>

07:06.894 --> 07:08.561
We have
a doctor's appointment.

07:08.563 --> 07:11.296
Vaccinations.

07:11.298 --> 07:12.831
Wait, another one?

07:12.833 --> 07:14.433
Yeah.
You can't move it?

07:14.435 --> 07:16.569
No, we gotta stay
on schedule.

07:16.571 --> 07:19.772
[ Sighs ] Alright,
well, next year, then.

07:19.774 --> 07:20.973
<i> Claro.</i>

07:20.975 --> 07:22.175
Hey, can you also
ask the doctor

07:22.177 --> 07:24.377
