in the ocean?

07:24.379 --> 07:24.977
Yeah.

07:24.979 --> 07:26.779
[ Baby crying ]

07:26.781 --> 07:30.649
I got him.

07:30.651 --> 07:33.652
[ Rock music playing ]

07:33.654 --> 07:34.853
He's late again.

07:34.855 --> 07:36.455
