for three people.

07:43.598 --> 07:45.798
I need help lifting the safe,
and you got to drive.

07:45.800 --> 07:47.266
Yeah, right,
right, right!

07:47.268 --> 07:50.002
I don't get why you guys
don't come together.

07:50.004 --> 07:51.536
You're sleeping
on his couch.

07:51.538 --> 07:53.538
