last night.
What?!

07:53.540 --> 07:55.308
I don't know.

07:57.745 --> 08:01.080
Jesus.

08:01.082 --> 08:03.015
[ Sighs ]

08:03.017 --> 08:05.150
Alright, well...

08:05.152 --> 08:07.286
what about you?

08:07.288 --> 08:09.222
Are you talking
to Cheryl,

08:09.224 --> 08:12.157
trying to get back
into the house?

08:12.159 --> 08:14.293
I'm not sure I want
back in the house.

08:14.295 --> 08:16.295
Why?
Aren't you sad?

08:18.099 --> 08:20.499
She's your wife.

08:20.501 --> 08:23.236
You don't have to spend
every night at Manny's house.

08:23.238 --> 08:25.838
[ People cheering ]

08:25.840 --> 08:29.642
I'm serious.

08:29.644 --> 08:31.844
Shit.

08:31.846 --> 08:33.578
Manny.

08:33.580 --> 08:37.049
