08:37.051 --> 08:39.051
What's going on?
I thought this thing
was happening.

08:39.053 --> 08:40.253
We hit a snag.

08:40.255 --> 08:41.454
Hit a snag?
No, no.

08:41.456 --> 08:43.522
Y-You said this
was gonna be simple.

08:43.524 --> 08:44.924
Linda, it<i> is</i>
gonna be simple.

08:44.926 --> 08:48.060
I put my ass on the line.

08:48.062 --> 08:50.663
Can we do it
next weekend?
No, no,
today was the day.

08:50.665 --> 08:52.465
All of the boys just
rotated out of Pendleton.

08:52.467 --> 08:55.868
Okay, well, if we're gonna do
this, we have to do it right.

08:55.870 --> 08:59.538
