09:08.749 --> 09:11.617
Just give me a call when
you think the time's right.

09:13.554 --> 09:16.155
How the kids liking
Sunnyview?

09:16.157 --> 09:17.356
It's school.
Yeah.

09:17.358 --> 09:19.024
I use it like daycare.

09:19.026 --> 09:20.359
Baz always wants to skip,

09:20.361 --> 09:22.227
but child services
are always popping in

09:22.229 --> 09:24.830
since their bitch of a grandma
called them on me.

09:24.832 --> 09:26.031
Free lunch, though.

09:26.033 --> 09:28.633
There is that.

09:28.635 --> 09:29.969
Alright.

09:29.971 --> 09:31.770
I'll be in touch.

09:31.772 --> 09:37.376
♪♪

09:37.378 --> 09:40.680
[ Up-tempo music playing,
indistinct conversations ]

09:43.318 --> 09:45.718
Look at these
pieces of shit.
Who?

09:45.720 --> 09:48.387
These assholes that opened up
that new bar down the street.

09:48.389 --> 09:49.922
Yeah, well,
Rob looks stoked.

09:49.924 --> 09:52.858
So stoked, bro.
Free shirt?

09:52.860 --> 09:54.193
Can't go wrong.

09:54.195 --> 09:56.795
Ugh. Libations?
Jesus.

09:56.797 --> 09:58.263
Free stuff.

09:58.265 --> 10:01.934
How about a, uh,
one -- one of those beers?

10:01.936 --> 10:03.402
Give the guy a beer.

10:03.404 --> 10:06.138
Oh, you're just swimming
in freebies today, bud.

10:06.140 --> 10:07.472
It's a good day.

10:07.474 --> 10:09.408
No, you're not wearing
this garbage.

10:09.410 --> 10:11.344
Well,
thanks for the beer.

10:14.749 --> 10:16.281
Diego: Sorry, man.

10:16.283 --> 10:17.750
Nice setup.

10:17.752 --> 10:19.084
Thanks.

10:19.086 --> 10:21.020
Hey, remember when
Pope used to skate?

10:21.022 --> 10:23.155
Craig: Yeah, he just
used to roll back and forth

10:23.157 --> 10:24.823
on that one ramp
all day and night.

10:24.825 --> 10:26.959
